item.title: Urgent client help
item.dc:creator: @Top_Glitch Top Glitch
item.description:
@Top_Glitch wrote:

Well, make sure everything is in a folder. Name the folder something like. “Client” Then make sure your complier and run are in where the main files are located. (So all the files, i.e client.java/class are all together)

If you’re extracting it, make sure everything is in a folder.
